<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us - GiftHub</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

       


       

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 3rem 1rem;
        }

        .content-wrapper {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .contact-info,
        .contact-form {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .contact-info h2,
        .contact-form h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .info-item {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            padding-bottom: 2rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .info-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .info-item h3 {
            color: #764ba2;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .info-item p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .info-item a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .info-item a:hover {
            color: #764ba2;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        input,
        textarea,
        select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            border: 2px solid #eee;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }

        input:focus,
        textarea:focus,
        select:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #667eea;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
        }

        textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 120px;
        }

        #send-message {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
            width: 100%;
        }

        button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }

        .faq-section {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .faq-section h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .faq-item {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .faq-item h4 {
            color: #764ba2;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .faq-item h4:hover {
            color: #667eea;
        }

        .faq-item p {
            color: #666;
            margin-left: 0;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

      

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .content-wrapper {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%-include('../partials/user/newheader.ejs') %>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <!-- Contact Information -->
            <div class="contact-info">
                <h2>Get in Touch</h2>

                <div class="info-item">
                    <h3>üìç Address</h3>
                    <p>123 Gift Street<br>
                        Shopping District<br>
                        New York, NY 10001<br>
                        United States</p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-item">
                    <h3>üìû Phone</h3>
                    <p><a href="tel:+1-800-123-4567">+1 (800) 123-4567</a><br>
                        Available Monday - Friday, 9 AM - 6 PM EST</p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-item">
                    <h3>‚úâÔ∏è Email</h3>
                    <p><a href="mailto:support@gifthub.com">support@gifthub.com</a><br>
                        <a href="mailto:orders@gifthub.com">orders@gifthub.com</a><br>
                        We typically respond within 24 hours
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-item">
                    <h3>üåê Follow Us</h3>
                    <p><a href="#">Facebook</a> | <a href="#">Instagram</a> | <a href="#">Twitter</a><br>
                        Connect with us on social media for special offers!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Contact Form -->
            <div class="contact-form">
                <h2>Send us a Message</h2>
                <form id="contactForm">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name">Full Name *</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
                        <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone">
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="subject">Subject *</label>
                        <select id="subject" name="subject" required>
                            <option value="">Select a subject...</option>
                            <option value="order">Order Inquiry</option>
                            <option value="delivery">Delivery Question</option>
                            <option value="return">Return & Refund</option>
                            <option value="gift-wrapping">Gift Wrapping</option>
                            <option value="custom">Custom Order</option>
                            <option value="other">Other</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="message">Message *</label>
                        <textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <button id="send-message" type="submit">Send Message</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Section -->
        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>‚ùì How long does delivery take?</h4>
                <p>Standard delivery typically takes 5-7 business days. We also offer express shipping (2-3 days) and
                    priority shipping (next day) for an additional fee.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>‚ùì Do you offer gift wrapping?</h4>
                <p>Yes! We provide complimentary gift wrapping with ribbon and a personalized message card with every
                    order. Premium gift wrapping options are also available.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>‚ùì What's your return policy?</h4>
                <p>We offer a 30-day return policy on all items. If you're not satisfied, simply contact our support
                    team to initiate a return. Refunds are processed within 5-7 business days.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>‚ùì Can I place a custom order?</h4>
                <p>Absolutely! For custom gifts and bulk orders, please email us at <a
                        href="mailto:orders@gifthub.com">orders@gifthub.com</a> or call our team to discuss your
                    specific needs.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>‚ùì Do you ship internationally?</h4>
                <p>Yes, we ship to over 50 countries worldwide. Shipping costs and delivery times vary by location.
                    Contact us for international shipping rates.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%-include('../partials/user/footer.ejs') %>
</body>

</html>